premise_source_doc_sentence: His research interests cover theories of international relations ; theories of global governance ; the history of thought on international relations ; comparative regionalism ; and the international relations of the Americas , with particular reference to Brazil .
International relations as a discipline is believed to have emerged after the First World War with the establishment of a Chair of International Relations at the University of Wales , Aberystwyth .
International relations theory is the study of international relations  (  IR  )  from a theoretical perspective .
Explanatory and constitutive approaches in international relations theory is a distinction made when classifying international relations theories .
